# Golden-file newline discipline (see docs/proof_lanes.md, Lane 7).
#
# Deterministic JSON/golden fixtures must be byte-identical across Linux, macOS,
# and Windows checkouts, so force LF and disable CRLF translation regardless of
# a contributor's core.autocrlf. The full cross-platform CI matrix and the
# "no golden contains \r" check are owned by bead
# fsnow-native-snowflake-connector-w0i.14.

# Normalize line endings for text by default.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Fixtures compared as raw bytes — pin LF explicitly.
*.json   text eol=lf
*.jsonl  text eol=lf
*.golden text eol=lf
*.toml   text eol=lf
*.md     text eol=lf
*.rs     text eol=lf
*.sh     text eol=lf

# Binary fixtures (e.g. gzip partition bodies) must never be munged.
*.gz   binary
*.gzip binary
*.der  binary
*.png  binary
